title: UE BOOM 2 - The 360-Degree Wireless Speaker With Insanely Great Sound
description: UE BOOM 2 is the 360-degree wireless speaker that blasts loud, insanely great sound with deep, powerful bass in every direction - everywhere you go. It was designed to get wet, muddy, and beat up. It’s waterproof, shockproof and crafted from the sexiest and most uninhibited premium materials in the known universe.
